{{Lunisolar March|qq=}}
'''March 22''' is the 22nd day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Taika|ja|大化|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|646|ja|646年|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|April 12|ja|4月12日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Sōsōryō|ja|薄葬令|qq=|12=draft}} is issued, prohibiting the construction of large tombs and the practice of having retainers commit ritual suicide upon their lord’s death.
* {{ill|Kōryaku|ja|康暦|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year / {{ill|Tenjū (Japan)|ja|天授 (日本)|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1379|ja|1379年|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The Northern Court changes the era name from {{ill|Eiwa (Japan)|ja|永和 (日本)|qq=|12=draft}} to {{ill|Kōryaku|ja|康暦|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1870|ja|1870年|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|April 22|ja|4月22日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Tokyo Prefecture (1868–1943)|ja|東京府|qq=|12=draft}} grants permission for the operation of {{ill|rickshaws|ja|人力車|qq=|12=draft}}.

